    "본문HTML": "<p>\n\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Gulim, 굴림, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px; word-break: keep-all; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\">『</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: -0.5px; font-weight: bold;\">리버럴아츠</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\">』 </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: -0.5px; font-weight: bold;\">제</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><font style='font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif;'>6</font></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><font face=\"함초롬바탕\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">권 </span></font><font style='font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif;'>1</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: -0.5px; font-weight: bold;\">호 논문모집 안내</span></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: center; word-break: keep-all; font-weight: bold;'> </p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">안녕하세요</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">?</span></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">동국대학교 다르마교양교육연구소가 교양교육 전문 학술지 </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">『</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">리버럴아츠</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">』 </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">제</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">권 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">호에 게재할 논문을 다음과 같이 모집하오니</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">교양교육에 관심이 있는 연구자 여러분의 많은 투고 바랍니다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'> </p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학술지명</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">『</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">리버럴아츠</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">』</span></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">논문 모집 분야</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">교양교육 관련 전 분야 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">대학의 교양교육 발전에 의미 있는 이론적 기여를 하거나</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">교육현장에서 인문</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">·</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">사회</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">이공학</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">예술</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">·</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">체육</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">융복합 등 다양한 분야의 교양교육을 실천하는 방법에 관한 이해를 넓힐 수 있는 교양교육 전반에 관한 내용</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">)</span></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'> </p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">3. </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">투고자격</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">교양교육에 관심이 있는 모든 연구자 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">박사과정생 이상</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">다만 석사과정생의 경우는 지도교수의 추천과 연구소장의 결정에 따라 공동저자로 투고할 수 있음</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">)</span></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'> </p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">4. </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">일정 및 방법</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Gulim, 굴림, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><strong><span style='font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0pt;'>1) </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">투고 마감일</span><span style='font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0pt;'>: </span><span style='font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold; text-decoration-line: underline;'>2026</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: -0.5px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration-line: underline;\">년</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><font style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.5px;\"> </span></font><font style='font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif;'>5</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: -0.5px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration-line: underline;\">월</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><font face=\"함초롬바탕\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.5px;\"> 2</span></font><font style='font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif;'>0</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: -0.5px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration-line: underline;\">일</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Gulim, 굴림, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><strong><span style='font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0pt;'>2) </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">발행 예정일</span><span style='font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0pt;'>: 2026</span><font face=\"함초롬바탕\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">년 </span></font><font style='font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif;'>6</font><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">월 </span><span style='font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0pt;'>30</span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">일</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'><span style=\"font-size:14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">3) </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">제출 방법</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">잼스 투고 </span><u><a href=\"https://libarts.jams.or.kr/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://libarts.jams.or.kr</a></u></strong></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'> </p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">5. </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">유의사항</span></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">1) </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">논문투고규정 및 원고작성규칙이 준수되지 않은 논문은 접수하지 않음</span></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">2) </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">미발표 논문이어야 하며</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">타 학술지와 중복 투고는 불가함</span></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"맑은 고딕\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 13.3333px;'><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">3) </span><span style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">투고 접수된 논문은 반환하지 않음</span></span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17